{"tid":1215363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"好奇一問 催淚彈同煙霧彈係落雨天用唔用到","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T07:39:29.000Z","uid":51819,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00a57ca19e838b2fd62713d1495388dbf6ff2feb","tid":1215363,"uid":51819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"我怕落雨會令警察先生執唔到法<br />\n我係中國人呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c403819c62592e0d3bb71b66066e010a29cc0d","tid":1215363,"uid":247463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"學術討論"},{"pid":"7d6833ff49c7729579ea072facef335357073264","tid":1215363,"uid":51819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人知"},{"pid":"6baecb0cf12115c6104e14d577dd74f86c836291","tid":1215363,"uid":131295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"效力會相對弱左但唔係冇，一般催淚氣體主要有效成份 2-chlorobenzalmalonitrile係不溶於水，所以唔會直接被雨溶走，但由於催淚彈係透過燃燒加熱隻有效成份先令佢變成氣體，所以有雨水會降低燃燒效果亦會沖走部分粒子<br />\n<br />\n但最有效都係用泳鏡之類嘅無空隙嘅眼部保護，加上3M工業級或以上防煙霧口罩，普通口罩眼罩保護效能幾低大家都有眼見"},{"pid":"193fb97711bbc53b7b798bb61b0e2b66201e843e","tid":1215363,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}